        "callDataGenerate": {
          "__version": "1.0",
          "schema": {
            "botStyle": "Professional",
            "maxTokens": 800,
            "model": null,
            "prompt": "Compose a comprehensive briefing document from the following information:\n\nKey Information: {{input.keyInfo}}\nContext/Background: {{input.context}}\nRecent Updates: {{input.recentUpdates}}\nUpcoming Items: {{input.upcomingItems}}\nAudience: {{input.audience}}\nBriefing Purpose: {{input.purpose}}\n\nCreate a well-structured briefing that includes:\n1. Executive Summary (3-5 bullet points)\n2. Key Highlights section\n3. Context and Background (if needed)\n4. Recent Developments or Updates\n5. Action Items or Decisions Needed\n6. Upcoming Milestones or Deadlines\n7. Risks or Issues to Monitor\n8. Recommendations (if applicable)\n9. Quick Reference or Key Metrics\n10. Next Steps\n\nFormat for clarity and scannability:\n- Use clear headings and subheadings\n- Include bullet points for easy scanning\n- Highlight critical information\n- Keep language concise and action-oriented\n- Prioritize information by importance\n\nReturn as structured JSON with keys: executiveSummary (array), keyHighlights (array), mainContent (object with sections), actionItems (array), upcomingMilestones (array), risks (array), recommendations (array), nextSteps (array).",
            "respondingBot": null
          }
        },
        "formInput": {
          "__version": "1.0",
          "schema": {
            "containers": [],
            "elements": [
              {
                "fieldName": "keyInfo",
                "id": "key_info_input",
                "label": "Key Information",
                "type": "Text",
                "isRequired": true,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "Main points to include in the briefing...",
                  "multiline": true,
                  "rows": 4
                }
              },
              {
                "fieldName": "context",
                "id": "context_input",
                "label": "Context/Background",
                "type": "Text",
                "isRequired": false,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "Relevant background information...",
                  "multiline": true,
                  "rows": 3
                }
              },
              {
                "fieldName": "recentUpdates",
                "id": "updates_input",
                "label": "Recent Updates",
                "type": "Text",
                "isRequired": false,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "What's new or changed recently?",
                  "multiline": true,
                  "rows": 2
                }
              },
              {
                "fieldName": "upcomingItems",
                "id": "upcoming_input",
                "label": "Upcoming Items",
                "type": "Text",
                "isRequired": false,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "Future events, deadlines, or milestones",
                  "multiline": true,
                  "rows": 2
